<subsection xml:id="C26.S14.SS2">
<title>Generating Functions</title>        
   
<para xml:id="C26.S14.SS2.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="96" xml:id="C26.S14.SS2.p1.s1">
 <Math equation-number="26.14.3" mode="display" xml:id="C26.S14.E3">\sum_{\sigma\in\mathfrak{S}_{n}}q^{\mathop{\mathrm{inv}}(\sigma)}=\sum_{\sigma \in\mathfrak{S}_{n}}q^{\mathop{\mathrm{maj}}(\sigma)}=\prod_{j=1}^{n}\frac{1-q ^{j}}{1-q}</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C26.S14.SS2.p2">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="97" xml:id="C26.S14.SS2.p2.s1">
 <Math equation-number="26.14.4" mode="display" xml:id="C26.S14.E4">\sum_{n,k=0}^{\infty}\genfrac{&lt;}{&gt;}{0.0pt}{}{n}{k}x^{k}\,\frac{t^{n}}{n!}= \frac{1-x}{\exp((x-1)t)-x}, if |x|&lt;1,|t|&lt;1</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>

 
<para xml:id="C26.S14.SS2.p3">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="98" xml:id="C26.S14.SS2.p3.s1">
 <Math equation-number="26.14.5" mode="display" xml:id="C26.S14.E5">\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\genfrac{&lt;}{&gt;}{0.0pt}{}{n}{k}\genfrac{(}{)}{0.0pt}{}{x+k}{n}=x ^{n}</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>

 
</subsection>
 
<subsection xml:id="C26.S14.SS3">
<title>Identities</title>        
   
<para xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p1">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="99" xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p1.s1">
In this subsection <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p1.m1">S\left(n,k\right)</Math> is again the Stirling number of the second kind (§26.8), and <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p1.m2">B_{m}</Math> is the <Math mode="inline" xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p1.m3">m</Math> th Bernoulli number (§24.2(i)).
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p2">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="100" xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p2.s1">
 <Math equation-number="26.14.6" mode="display" xml:id="C26.S14.E6">\genfrac{&lt;}{&gt;}{0.0pt}{}{n}{k}=\sum_{j=0}^{k}(-1)^{j}\genfrac{(}{)}{0.0pt}{}{n+ 1}{j}(k+1-j)^{n}, if n\geq 1,</Math> 
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p3">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="101" xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p3.s1">
 <Math equation-number="26.14.7" mode="display" xml:id="C26.S14.E7">\genfrac{&lt;}{&gt;}{0.0pt}{}{n}{k}=\sum_{j=0}^{n-k}(-1)^{n-k-j}j!\genfrac{(}{)}{0.0 pt}{}{n-j}{k}S\left(n,j\right),</Math> 
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p4">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="102" xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p4.s1">
 <Math equation-number="26.14.8" mode="display" xml:id="C26.S14.E8">\genfrac{&lt;}{&gt;}{0.0pt}{}{n}{k}=(k+1)\genfrac{&lt;}{&gt;}{0.0pt}{}{n-1}{k}+(n-k) \genfrac{&lt;}{&gt;}{0.0pt}{}{n-1}{k-1}, if n\geq 2,</Math> 
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p5">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="103" xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p5.s1">
 <Math equation-number="26.14.9" mode="display" xml:id="C26.S14.E9">\genfrac{&lt;}{&gt;}{0.0pt}{}{n}{k}=\genfrac{&lt;}{&gt;}{0.0pt}{}{n}{n-1-k}, if n\geq 1,</Math> 
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p6">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="104" xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p6.s1">
 <Math equation-number="26.14.10" mode="display" xml:id="C26.S14.E10">\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\genfrac{&lt;}{&gt;}{0.0pt}{}{n}{k}=n!, if n\geq 1</Math>.
</sentence>

</para>
 
<para xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p7">

<sentence sentence-num-in-para="1" sentence-num-in-section="105" xml:id="C26.S14.SS3.p7.s1">
